title: Dwayne Haskins unclaimed on waivers, Dolphins QB dilemma and the real NFL MVP (Football 12/30)
description:
Will Brinson and Brady Quinn connect for the final time in 2020 to talk about New Year's resolutions, or rather, their dislike of them. When the guys finally get to football, they react to the entire Dwayne Haskins saga with the latest development of the news he went unclaimed on waivers. They also tackle the argument of rest vs. rust that is back at the forefront this week as it usually is in Week 17. Will and Brady ponder Miami's thought process with the QB changes and dish out who they think deserves the MVP this season.
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
